’Щ@e30ac8359302ff353e4a5437be4e5aa15d4e9400a504c884d7aa3ce364938a9eЪнTitle: title: math median
Path: Examples
Content:
Compute the median of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [3 8 9 12 12 15] | math median
10.5

```
Compute the medians of the columns of a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [{a: 1 b: 3} {a: 2 b: -1} {a: -3 b: 5}] | math median
в•­в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”¬в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•®
в”‚ a в”‚ 1 в”‚
в”‚ b в”‚ 3 в”‚
в•°в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ґв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв•Ї

```
Find the median of a list of file sizes.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [5KB 10MB 200B] | math median
5.0 kB

```
